奧雲：「多謝賓施馬，多得佢，我先加盟到曼聯！費Sir話我知，當年佢簽唔到賓施馬先會簽我！」<br />
<br />
英文原文：&quot;I thank Benzema because without him I would never have gone to Manchester United,&quot; he admitted to Canal+, as quoted by Goal. &quot;Ferguson told me that I will only sign if he couldn't get Benzema. And that's what happened.&quot;
